OL,3,CSon of Norway's Crown Princess jailed
OL,4,Cfor four years after rape conviction
OL,6,FThe eldest son of Norway's Crown
OL,7,FPrincess Mette-Marit was sentenced to
OL,8,Ffour years in prison on Monday after
OL,9,Fbeing convicted of rape.
OL,11,FMarius Borg Hoiby, 29, was found
OL,12,Fguilty of two of the four rape charges
OL,13,Fhe was facing and acquitted of the
OL,14,Fother two.
OL,16,FHe was also convicted of assault and
OL,17,Fabuse in close relationships. In
OL,18,Faddition to the prison sentence, Hoiby
OL,19,Fwas ordered to pay compensation to the
OL,20,Fvictims.
OL,26,@sD@No|zD@co|
