OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1781549299
OL,3,CSon of Norway's Crown Princess jailed
OL,4,Cfor four years after rape conviction
OL,6,FHe is the stepson of the heir to the
OL,7,FNorwegian throne, Crown Prince Haakon,
OL,8,Fand is the son of Mette-Marit from a
OL,9,Fprevious relationship. He has no royal
OL,10,Ftitle or official duties.
OL,12,FHoiby had been charged with sexually
OL,13,Fassaulting four women who were asleep
OL,14,For otherwise unable to resist between
OL,15,F2018 and 2024.
OL,17,FHe faced a total of 40 criminal
OL,18,Fcharges, including some for lesser
OL,19,Foffences, such as assault, drug-
OL,20,Frelated crimes and violations of a
OL,21,Frestraining order.
OL,26,@tD@Bo|
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/4
