PN,31603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1781549299
OL,3,CSon of Norway's Crown Princess jailed
OL,4,Cfor four years after rape conviction
OL,6,FHoiby had denied the rape allegations
OL,7,Fbut admitted to several of the lesser
OL,8,Foffences.
OL,10,FProsecutors had asked Oslo District
OL,11,FCourt to sentence him to seven years
OL,12,Fand seven months in prison, while
OL,13,Fdefense lawyers had argued that he
OL,14,Fshould be acquitted of the rape
OL,15,Fallegations and receive no more than
OL,16,F18 months for offences he had admitted
OL,17,Fto.
OL,19,FThe sentence is not final and Hoiby
OL,20,Fcan still appeal.
OL,26,@nD@Bo|{D@`o|
