PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1781549299
OL,3,CSon of Norway's Crown Princess jailed
OL,4,Cfor four years after rape conviction
OL,6,FHoiby was not present in court on
OL,7,FMonday because of health reasons. He
OL,8,Fwatched the reading of the verdict via
OL,9,Fa video link from prison.
OL,11,FThe six-week trial concluded in March
OL,12,Fafter testimony from multiple accusers
OL,13,Fand presentation of evidence,
OL,14,Fincluding messages, images and videos
OL,15,Ffrom Hoiby's cellphone.
